snippet.title: What's Michael? (ホワッツマイケル?) for the NEC PC-88
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

MSX
PC-98


Game description:

What's Michael? is a Japanese-style adventure game based on the manga by Makoto Kobayashi, which was also turned into an anime.

Michael is an orange American Shorthair tabby cat, He is basically a feline version of the everyman.
